Notes: Ripon wins seventh consecutive game against Illinois College...Ripon leads
all-time series 29-14...Ripon's Maggie Oimoen becomes just the ninth player in
program history to score 1,000 career points...Oimoen records fourth
consecutive and 13th career double-double (21 points, 12 rebounds)
Game.Officials: Jodi Duffe,  Mike Lagrasso,  and Krystal Ellis
